### Create a new product
POST http://localhost:8080/api/produits
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nom": "Smartphone Y",
  "prixUnitaire": 499.99,
  "stockDisponible": 25
}

### Get product by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/produits/2

### Search products (pagination + filters)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/produits?start=0&size=10&nom=phone&prixMin=100&prixMax=600&stockMin=1&stockMax=100

### Search products (pagination only)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/produits?start=0&size=5

### Update a product
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/produits/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nom": "Smartphone X (2025)",
  "prixUnitaire": 529.99,
  "stockDisponible": 30
}

### Delete a product
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/produits/1
